msgctxt "Talk00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Thanks to your break-in at the bandits'\n"
"hideout, they spread their forces thin\n"
"looking for you.\n"
"It was just the opening I needed to bust\n"
"out and return here. <2.pa>I owe you my life!<3.ra><4.so>Seriously... "
"<5.pa>If you hadn't shown up...<6.pa>\n"
"Best case scenario, I'd have been\n"
"doomed to an all-banana diet."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: raw
#. 3: sound
msgctxt "Talk01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>It WAS you who saved me, right?\n"
"I'm not mistaken?<2.ra>I was so frustrated after being captured\n"
"that your face didn't quite register with\n"
"me, but I definitely remember your voice.\n"
"<3.so>You have no idea how embarrassed I am\n"
"for getting an outsider caught up in our\n"
"business.\n"
"After the stern talking-to I got from my\n"
"captain, I think I'll stay on my best\n"
"behavior for a while."
msgstr ""

